                    <p>There is a <strong>$100/month</strong> investiment to receive groups of diners at your restaurant from our nonprofit partners. All restaurants start at a trial level, with a <strong>50% discount</strong>, until we are able to send you a sufficient volume of diners per month (at least eight groups). At that point we bump you up to a regular membership, allowing you to <strong>add charities</strong> you want to support to the platform and to become a <strong>premium catering vendor</strong>.</p>
